5 I stumbled on Z Pizza in San Diego as it was close to the corporate office I was working out of. I was in love immediately, and when I saw that they had one near my house...I about died.  I absolutely 100% love places that serve items that normally are the farthest thing from healthy but make them healthy so that you feel so good eating it. Z Pizza is one of those places, and it manages to do it fairly cheap and quickly.   I stopped in one day to see if this location would be just as good as the San Diego one. It was. My veggie calzone with whole wheat crust was divine. I also love that this location delivers and you can order online. Score! I've taken friends from out of town here and they are always sorely disappointed that there isn't a Z Pizza where they live. Soon. I hope Z Pizza takes over the world.
