5 Yum, yum and more yum. And....they deliver!!!!!!!!  I have not met a pizza from Z Pizza that I don't adore. My faves are the ZBQ (barbecue chicken pizza) and Thai (delicious peanut sauce). I am personally a fan of the whole wheat crust, although not for dieting reasons...I really just think it tastes good!  I also really love their caesar salad. They are smart enough to do dressing on the side for delivery, so it stays crisp, not soggy. We've had the pizza bread sticks, too, which aren't half bad.   When I'm in the mood for delivery, I always go to Z Pizza. When we're dining out, I simply can't cheat on Patsy's. There's just something about their tomato sauce and basil...anyway, I shouldn't be talking about Patsy's in the review for Z Pizza, especially since I really do enjoy Z Pizza. I just love the fact that they deliver non-greasy and inventive pizza. Way better than Papa John's for sure.
